{"comments":"Composition Node — The composition tree structure.\n\nA Node is one layer in the composition. The tree structure:\n\n```\nComposition\n  └─ Node (background canvas)\n  └─ Node (viewport - bento layout)\n      └─ Node (card 1)\n          └─ Node (diffusion source with matte)\n          └─ Node (text overlay)\n      └─ Node (card 2)\n  └─ Node (floating button)\n      └─ triggers: [onHover → elevate, onPress → action]\n```\n\n## Layer Model\n\nEach node has:\n- Source: what generates pixels\n- Matte: shape that clips the source\n- Effects: stack of visual effects\n- Blend: how to composite with layers below\n- Transform: 2D/3D positioning\n- Triggers: event-driven behaviors\n- Children: nested nodes (for groups)\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Composition","Node"],"Layer"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[210,14],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Composition/Node.purs","start":[210,3]},"title":"NodeLayer"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Composition","Node"],"Layer"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[211,14],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Composition/Node.purs","start":[211,3]},"title":"NodeGroup"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[212,14],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Composition/Node.purs","start":[212,3]},"title":"NodeEmpty"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Composition","Node"],"Node"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[214,34],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Composition/Node.purs","start":[214,1]},"title":"eqNode"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"insta